          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1634039929348-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are in the oven, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop the<strong> red onions</strong> roughly</p><p>Top, tail and chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> roughly into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1634039937478-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1634039937478-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1634039937478-x700.jpg",
